data.description: Both practical and chic, this modern home design delivers standout style with a versatile layout. The open floor plan of the main level invites casual entertaining, with room for guests to sit at the kitchen's island. More than just a space for cooking and eating, the kitchen is where all of the action in the home takes place. It's the true heart of the home. The spacious, open living room is focused around the stunning fireplace. The living areas are light and bright with tons of windows. Secondary bedrooms and the game room are all located upstairs.  James Hardie fiber cement siding, tankless hot water heater and Energy Star rated HVAC are among the homes "green" features. Don't miss the opportunity to live in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in the Mustang/Yukon area. Look no further, you've just found your new house! Welcome Home.
